comments: McDaniels (MIN) places a resting forearm to Morant's (MEM) side as they mutually engage and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Russell (MIN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
McDaniels (MIN) jumps alongside of Morant's (MEM) path and any leg to leg contact is deemed incidental as he legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) brushes Clarke's (MEM) arm and marginal contact occurs on the release, which does not affect the putback shot attempt at the basket.
Bane (MEM) is established in Towns' (MIN) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he absorbs the contact during the drive.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and McDaniels (MIN) come together and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Russell (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

McDaniels (MIN) moves alongside of and absorbs the marginal contact created by Jackson Jr. (MEM) as he brings his arms into a vertical position during the driving shot attempt. Towns (MIN) makes clean ball contact to block the shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) moves alongside of Morant (MEM) and absorbs the marginal contact before making clean ball contact to temporarily dislodge it.
Towns (MIN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the offensive player loses control of the ball.
McDaniels (MIN) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) taps the rebound out and is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The Timberwolves are correctly awarded possession.
Williams (MEM) and Edwards (MIN) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs during the inbounds play.
Bane (MEM) and Konchar (MEM) make clean ball contact as they pursue the loose ball and any follow-through contact with Towns (MIN) is deemed incidental.
Replay review of the out-of-bounds called on Bane (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  Towns (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Morant's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Morant's (MEM) shot does not touch the basket and goes directly out of bounds without being touched by any other player. Possession is correctly awarded to the Timberwolves.
Clarke (MEM) briefly grasps and immediately releases McDaniels' (MIN) jersey as marginal contact occurs, which does not affect his ability to get to the inbounds pass.
During the screen, Bane (MEM) and Russell (MIN) briefly engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Clarke (MEM) commits a take foul on McDaniels (MIN).
